01:27:17,708 --> 01:27:20,500
You were tearin' boards
off that shed.

1024
01:27:21,292 --> 01:27:23,208
How could you remember that?

1025
01:27:23,292 --> 01:27:26,125
You were seven years old.
You were scared to death.

1026
01:27:26,167 --> 01:27:30,042
What I remember is that you were
holding that thing when you hugged me.

1027
01:27:30,125 --> 01:27:33,208
When you dropped it,
it made this loud clanging sound.

1028
01:27:33,292 --> 01:27:34,958
Like this?

1029
01:27:38,417 --> 01:27:40,625
Why are you doing this?

1030
01:27:40,708 --> 01:27:46,167
Trying to tear my family apart
just because you lost your own parents.

1031
01:27:46,292 --> 01:27:48,417
- She wasn't--
- She's not foolin' anybody...

1032
01:27:48,542 --> 01:27:50,792
with that wide-eyed, innocent--

1033
01:27:50,833 --> 01:27:52,792
Do you know
what she's implying?

1034
01:27:52,875 --> 01:27:55,917
Even if I did have
one of those things in my hands...

1035
01:27:56,042 --> 01:27:59,125
that doesn't mean there wasn't another
at the bottom of the stairs.

1036
01:28:00,000 --> 01:28:02,292
You remember that day.

1037
01:28:02,333 --> 01:28:05,292
You remember the fall.

1038
01:28:05,375 --> 01:28:07,792
That fall could've killed
anybody who--

1039
01:28:11,458 --> 01:28:15,958
Why, no one's implying
that you killed Jack. My God!

1040
01:28:16,042 --> 01:28:19,292
Lots of wives have affairs
and don't kill their husbands...

1041
01:28:19,458 --> 01:28:21,792
because he finds out
and is gonna leave her.

1042
01:28:21,917 --> 01:28:24,167
My father was
having the affair.

1043
01:28:24,208 --> 01:28:28,250
Oh, no. You got that backwards.
Robin Hayes was a horse wrangler.

1044
01:28:28,333 --> 01:28:32,083
Martha was having
an affair with him.

1045
01:28:32,167 --> 01:28:35,958
Alice told you that,
didn't she?

1046
01:28:36,000 --> 01:28:39,375
That's Just the kind of twisted lie
Alice would invent...

1047
01:28:39,417 --> 01:28:42,667
and your wife would try to perpetuate
to turn you against me.

1048
01:28:42,708 --> 01:28:46,417
- Don't you see what she's doing?
- 412-263-1841.

1049
01:28:46,500 --> 01:28:49,708
I just talked to Robin Hayes.
He's expecting the call.

1050
01:28:49,750 --> 01:28:53,208
Would you like to speak to him
for old time's sake?

1051
01:28:54,417 --> 01:28:58,208
Robin Hayes died last year
of a heart attack.

1052
01:28:58,250 --> 01:29:00,250
There's one you didn't cause.

1053
01:29:01,542 --> 01:29:05,958
You Just couldn't bear
to let a happy family be, could you?

1054
01:29:09,125 --> 01:29:12,167
We were so close to being happy.

1055
01:29:14,417 --> 01:29:17,875
Here's how close we were.

1056
01:29:20,542 --> 01:29:23,083
Your mother tried to kill me
last night.

1057
01:29:23,208 --> 01:29:26,375
- That's a lie.
- Nobody leaves Martha.

1058
01:29:26,458 --> 01:29:30,083
Don't you see? Your father was leaving.
That's why she killed him.

1059
01:29:30,167 --> 01:29:34,542
And what's worse, she made you,
her own child, think that he did it...

1060
01:29:34,583 --> 01:29:38,917
so that she could bind you to her
for the rest of your life!

1061
01:29:38,958 --> 01:29:43,667
I want you to throw this lying bitch
out of my house!

1062
01:29:43,708 --> 01:29:47,000
There's only room
for one of those.

1063
01:29:47,083 --> 01:29:50,875
- You'll never prove anything.
- She doesn't have to.

1064
01:29:54,167 --> 01:29:57,500
- Oh, but Jackson, you can't--
- Shut up!

1065
01:29:59,917 --> 01:30:02,708
Everything about you is a lie.

1066
01:30:03,708 --> 01:30:07,375
This place and everything in it
will be sold.

1067
01:30:07,458 --> 01:30:12,000
You will never see me
or any member of my family again.

1068
01:30:14,458 --> 01:30:16,833
But I did it all for you.

1069
01:30:16,917 --> 01:30:20,000
You are not my mother.

1070
01:30:29,083 --> 01:30:30,875
You did this.

1071
01:30:30,917 --> 01:30:35,042
You tricked him! You trapped him!
You got yourself pregnant!

1072
01:30:35,875 --> 01:30:37,792
I know what you're after.

1073
01:30:37,875 --> 01:30:40,958
You want my farm, my land...

1074
01:30:41,042 --> 01:30:42,458
my boy!

1075
01:30:45,042 --> 01:30:48,750
You want to take everything I have
and leave me with nothing!

1076
01:30:48,792 --> 01:30:51,042
Don't you see what she's doing?

1077
01:30:53,458 --> 01:30:55,375
She wants to be me.

1078
01:31:07,958 --> 01:31:09,958
So long, Martha.

1079
01:31:53,417 --> 01:31:54,833
Grandma.

